 Indonesia version English version  INDONESIA FadeOut function Metode fadeout () secara bertahap mengubah opacity, untuk elemen yang dipilih, dari terlihat hingga tersembunyi (efek memudar).
Elemen tersembunyi tidak akan ditampilkan sama sekali.
Durasi waktu dapat diberikan dalam milidetik untuk menentukan berapa lama animasi akan berjalan.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btni&#34; value=&#34;fadeOut&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1i&#34; style=&#34;background:red;width:100px;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btni&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1i&quot;).fadeOut(2000); //5seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btni").click(function() { $("#d1i").fadeOut(2000); //5seconds }); });   FadeIn function Metode fadein () secara bertahap mengubah opacity, untuk elemen yang dipilih, dari tersembunyi untuk terlihat.
Elemen harus disembunyikan sebelum menggunakan fungsi ini, itu satu-satunya cara kita dapat memberi tahu perubahan.
Durasi waktu dapat diberikan dalam milidetik untuk menentukan berapa lama animasi akan berjalan.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn2i&#34; value=&#34;fadeIn&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&quot;d2i&quot; style=&quot;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&quot;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn2i&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d2i&quot;).hide(); //If you not hide it you can't able to see the changes  $(&quot;#d2i&quot;).fadeIn(2000); //2seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn2i").click(function() { $("#d2i").hide(); //If you not hide it you can't able to see the changes $("#d2i").fadeIn(2000); //2seconds }); });   FadeToggle function Metode fadetoggle () mengubah antara fadein () dan fadeout () metode.
Jika elemen-elemennya memudar, fadetoggle () akan memudar mereka.
Jika elemen-elemennya memudar, fadetoggle () akan memudar mereka.
Durasi waktu dapat diberikan dalam milidetik untuk menentukan berapa lama animasi akan berjalan.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn3i&#34; value=&#34;fadeToggle&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d3i&#34; style=&#34;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn3i&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d3i&quot;).fadeToggle(2000); //2seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn3i").click(function() { $("#d3i").fadeToggle(2000); //2seconds }); });   FadeTo function Metode fadeto () secara bertahap mengubah opacity, untuk elemen yang dipilih, ke opacity tertentu (efek memudar).
Durasi waktu dan opacity yang ditentukan harus diberikan pada milidetik untuk menentukan berapa lama animasi akan berjalan.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn4&#34; value=&#34;fadeTo&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d4&#34; style=&#34;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn4&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d4&quot;).fadeTo(2000, 0.2); //2seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn4i").click(function() { $("#d4i").fadeTo(2000, 0.2); //2seconds }); });    ENGLISH FadeOut function The fadeOut() method gradually changes the opacity, for selected elements, from visible to hidden (fading effect).
Hidden elements will not be displayed at all.
The time duration can be given in milliseconds to determine how long the animation will run.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn&#34; value=&#34;fadeOut&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34; style=&#34;background:red;width:100px;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).fadeOut(2000); //5seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn").click(function() { $("#d1").fadeOut(2000); //5seconds }); });   FadeIn function The fadeIn() method gradually changes the opacity, for selected elements, from hidden to visible.
The element should be hidden before using this function, it is the only way we can notify the changes.
The time duration can be given in milliseconds to determine how long the animation will run.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn2&#34; value=&#34;fadeIn&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&quot;d2&quot; style=&quot;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&quot;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn2&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d2&quot;).hide(); //If you not hide it you can't able to see the changes  $(&quot;#d2&quot;).fadeIn(3000); //3seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn2").click(function() { $("#d2").hide(); //If you not hide it you can't able to see the changes $("#d2").fadeIn(3000); //3seconds }); });   FadeToggle function The fadeToggle() method toggles between the fadeIn() and fadeOut() methods.
If the elements are faded out, fadeToggle() will fade them in.
If the elements are faded in, fadeToggle() will fade them out.
The time duration can be given in milliseconds to determine how long the animation will run.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn3&#34; value=&#34;fadeToggle&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d3&#34; style=&#34;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn3&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d3&quot;).fadeToggle(2000); //2seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn3").click(function() { $("#d3").fadeToggle(2000); //2seconds }); });   FadeTo function The fadeTo() method gradually changes the opacity, for selected elements, to a specified opacity (fading effect).
The time duration and the specified opacity should be given in milliseconds to determine how long the animation will run.
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn4&#34; value=&#34;fadeTo&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d4&#34; style=&#34;background:grey;width:100%;height:100px&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn4&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d4&quot;).fadeTo(2000, 0.2); //2seconds  }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 This is the Div   $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn4").click(function() { $("#d4").fadeTo(2000, 0.2); //2seconds }); });

 English version Indonesia version  English hide and show jQuery The hide() function is used to hide any element using its Id or classname. In this example we are hiding the div element.
The show() function is used to show any hidden element using its Id or classname. In this example, we are showing the div element which was dynamically hidden in the design itself.
example Hide
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;hdbtn&#34; value=&#34;Hide&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;== jQuery file &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#hdbtn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).hide(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
Show
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;shbtn&#34; value=&#34;Show&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34; style=&#34;display:none;&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#shbtn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).show(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.    $(document).ready(function() { $("#hdbtn").click(function() { $("#d1").hide(); }); });    $(document).ready(function() { $("#shbtn").click(function() { $("#d1").show(); }); });   hide and show toggle() The toggle() method toggles between hide() and show() for the selected elements. This method checks the selected elements for visibility. show() is run if an element is hidden. hide() is run if an element is visible - This creates a toggle effect.
example &lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn&#34; value=&#34;Show/Hide&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).toggle(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.    $(document).ready(function() { $("#btn").click(function() { $("#d2").toggle(); }); });   Indonesia sembunyikan dan tampilkan jQuery Fungsi hide() digunakan untuk menyembunyikan elemen apa pun menggunakan Id atau classname-nya. Dalam contoh ini kita menyembunyikan elemen div.
Fungsi show() digunakan untuk menampilkan elemen tersembunyi menggunakan Id atau classname. Dalam contoh ini, kami menunjukkan elemen div yang tersembunyi secara dinamis dalam desain itu sendiri.
contoh Bersembunyi
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;hdbtn&#34; value=&#34;Hide&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;== jQuery file &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#hdbtn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).hide(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
Menunjukkan
&lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;shbtn&#34; value=&#34;Show&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34; style=&#34;display:none;&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#shbtn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).show(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.    $(document).ready(function() { $("#hdbtni").click(function() { $("#i1").hide(); }); });    $(document).ready(function() { $("#shbtni").click(function() { $("#i1").show(); }); });   sembunyikan dan tampilkan toggle() Metode toggle() beralih antara hide() dan show() untuk elemen yang dipilih. Metode ini memeriksa elemen yang dipilih untuk visibilitas. show() dijalankan jika elemen disembunyikan. hide() dijalankan jika elemen terlihat - Ini menciptakan efek sakelar.
contoh &lt;input type=&#34;button&#34; id=&#34;btn&#34; value=&#34;Show/Hide&#34;&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;d1&#34;&gt;This is the Div&lt;/div&gt; &lt;script src=&quot;js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script&gt; $(document).ready(function() { $(&quot;#btn&quot;).click(function() { $(&quot;#d1&quot;).toggle(); }); }); &lt;/script&gt;
 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.    $(document).ready(function() { $("#btni").click(function() { $("#i2").toggle(); }); });
